                </p>

                <ul class="list-unstyled d-flex flex-column gap-3 mb-5">
                    <li class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-4 border" style="background:#f8fafc;border-color:#e2e8f0 !important;">
                        <div class="rounded-3 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fw-black flex-shrink-0" style="width:32px;height:32px;font-size:1.1rem;background-color:#0f172a;color:#fff;"><i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-down-fill"></i></div>
                        <span class="fw-black small" style="color:#0f172a;">One-Click Anki (.apkg) Universal Import</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-4 border" style="background:#f0f9ff;border-color:#bae6fd !important;">
                        <div class="rounded-3 text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fw-black flex-shrink-0" style="width:32px;height:32px;font-size:1.1rem;background-color:#0ea5e9;box-shadow:0 2px 0 #0284c7;"><i class="bi bi-stopwatch-fill"></i></div>
                        <span class="fw-black small" style="color:#0f172a;">Adaptive Algorithmic Recall Timing</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-4 border" style="background:#fffbeb;border-color:#fde68a !important;">
                        <div class="rounded-3 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fw-black flex-shrink-0 bg-transparent" style="width:32px;height:32px;">
                            <div class="gold-coin" style="width:22px;height:22px;font-size:0.65rem;border-width:2px;box-shadow:0 2px 0 #b45309;margin:0;"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="fw-black small" style="color:#0f172a;">Earn live EXP &amp; Gold for every single review flip</span>
                    </li>
